Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海鞘是石卷市的名產
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是石卷市出身的所以這是我的最愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯不錯~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您的誇獎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是你 真的不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不挑食？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過不要單說好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能有更加豐富的語言表現就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼下次也拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託您了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一時我的心都快冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實波的圓場太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實波 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真的覺得好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被導演說了只是覺得好吃並不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是「Wake Up. Girls!」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我們來到了僊台的牛舌店
