Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:35.13,up-center,NTP,0,0,30,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}因為我就是唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
